
New Features in taskd 0.7.0

  - Optional SSL support.  May be turned off for debugging or private use, but
    is not a good idea.

  Please refer to the ChangeLog file for full details.  There are too many to
  list here.

New configuration options in taskd 0.7.0

  - They are all new

---

Taskd has been built and tested on the following configurations:

  * OS X 10.8 Mountain Lion

---

While taskd has undergone testing, bugs are sure to remain.  If you encounter a
bug, please enter a new issue at:

  http://taskwarrior.org/projects/taskwarrior/issues/new

Or you can also report the issue in the forums at:

  http://taskwarrior.org/projects/taskwarrior/boards

Or just send a message to:

  support@taskwarrio.org

Thank you.

